SECTION 10: PERFORMANCE METRICS (Exam May Reference)
================================================================================

Task Success Rate = (Successful Completions / Total Attempts) × 100%
Average Response Time = Σ(Response Times) / Number of Requests
Tool Call Efficiency = Successful Tool Calls / Total Tool Calls
Memory Utilization = Used Context Tokens / Max Context Tokens
Escalation Rate = Human Escalations / Total Requests (lower = better)
Throughput = Requests Processed / Time Period
Cost per Request = (Inference Cost + Infrastructure Cost) / Total Requests


